{"word":"ἐκφορέω","slug":"ἐκφορέω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<entryFree id=\"n33194\" key=\"e)kfore/w\" type=\"main\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"entryFree\"> <orth extent=\"suff\" lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"orth\">ἐκφορ-έω</orth>,= <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ἐκφέρω</foreign>, <sense id=\"n33194.0\" n=\"A\" level=\"1\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">carry out</tr_>, as a corpse for burial, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg002.perseus-grc1:22:451\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Od.\">Od.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">22.451</biblScope></bibl>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg002.perseus-grc1:24:417\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">24.417</biblScope> </bibl> (tm.). </sense> <sense n=\"2\" id=\"n33194.1\" level=\"3\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> generally, <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">carry out</tr_>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0016.tlg001.perseus-grc1:1:197\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Hdt.\">Hdt.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">1.197</biblScope></bibl>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0016.tlg001.perseus-grc1:9:116\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">9.116</biblScope></bibl>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0017.tlg006.perseus-grc1:42\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Is.\">Is.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">6.42</biblScope> </bibl> (<gramGrp opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gramGrp\"> <gram type=\"voice\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gram\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Pass.\">Pass.</a></gram></gramGrp>, ib.<bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0017.tlg001.perseus-grc1:41\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">41</biblScope> </bibl>):—<gramGrp opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gramGrp\"> <gram type=\"voice\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gram\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Med.\">Med.</a></gram></gramGrp>, <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">take out with one</tr_>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0006.tlg001.perseus-grc1:234\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ E.\">E.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Cyc.\">Cyc.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">234</biblScope></bibl>, etc.:— <gramGrp opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gramGrp\"> <gram type=\"voice\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gram\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Pass.\">Pass.</a></gram></gramGrp>, <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">move forth</tr_>, <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">ὣς τότε ταρφειαὶ κόρυθες . . νηῶν ἐκφορέοντο</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:19:360\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Il.\">Il.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">19.360</biblScope></bibl></cit>. </sense> <sense n=\"3\" id=\"n33194.2\" level=\"3\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">dig out</tr_>, of earth dug from a trench, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0016.tlg001.perseus-grc1:2:150\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Hdt.\">Hdt.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">2.150</biblScope> </bibl> (<gramGrp opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gramGrp\"> <gram type=\"voice\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gram\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Pass.\">Pass.</a></gram> </gramGrp>), <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0016.tlg001.perseus-grc1:7:23\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">7.23</biblScope> </bibl>; of metal from mines, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0032.tlg011.perseus-grc1:4:2\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ X.\">X.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Vect.\">Vect.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform